{"tid":1468644,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[抛磚引玉] 係時候整理戰線","createTime":"2019-08-13T19:38:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T19:44:01.000Z","uid":255280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"80a464a0003fc480a9ea4cdbd2a322b7649278e9","tid":1468644,"uid":255280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:38:20.000Z","msg":"由六月開始發生左一連串事件(林奠你條仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，當中我哋可以發現由一開始我哋只係開左反送中一條戰線，到依家戰線多到十隻手指數唔曬，身邊開始有人覺得戰線太多覺得混亂。所以我希望各位巴絲一齊幫手，理清思路確定戰線，對政府轉移視線既戰略實行一次反擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。暫時我諗到既有以下幾條：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n一，警察濫權、濫捕、使用過份武力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n二，政府修例非撤回決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n三，雙真普選<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n四，針對政府各種企圖嫁禍示威者之行為，例如機管局停Check-in服務但無取消航班<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n五，對反修例人士之控罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n六，政府暴動定性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n七，中共對海外華人文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span><br />\n</span><br />\n仲會唔會有其他戰線? 同埋戰線定好左我哋可以點做?<br />\n我相信和理非都可以出到力，勇武有勇武既玩法，和理非一樣有和理非既玩法。<br />\n最重要係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">兄弟爬山 各自努力，永不割蓆</span></span>"},{"pid":"38596c5bd8e39cfccccdfb74705e777493ea7677","tid":1468644,"uid":255280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:42:28.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"43f6d2868dceb24a3d1a4726e789f5b0030db998","tid":1468644,"uid":255280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:42:38.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"29fab93a11bf388bd2663d5cb84cc7ef55734255","tid":1468644,"uid":255280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:42:50.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"8b1150da18887000eceb4b17d811dbcea0ae8e10","tid":1468644,"uid":255280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:43:00.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"c54a260eece8adddcd4ea29bba7666aac34c2aa9","tid":1468644,"uid":255280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:43:11.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"6e3e3d58a8e8fc541a56092158a4f71d49b273ea","tid":1468644,"uid":255280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:43:21.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"f47caf534ffa795045dd45f10ba68f4b5508d274","tid":1468644,"uid":255280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:43:31.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"867965735d8c221f6cae601c649c752f776f9894","tid":1468644,"uid":255280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:43:41.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"84c4cb4b2bbf53f0b1f557d58e5c9cb922b5f3cc","tid":1468644,"uid":255280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:43:51.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"06d28ec9136d7c44cd9e1bd47b7e8d18995b17bf","tid":1468644,"uid":255280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:44:01.000Z","msg":"10"}]}